Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,S-A-W-A-G-E Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,S-A-W-A-G-E Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:17.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,SAWAGE LIFE Saturday night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:21.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sunday morning kanashimu\Nkoto wa nai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,SAWAGE LIFE Saturday night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:30.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omoikkiri hachamecha\Nni ashita wa nichiyoubi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:34.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ara que ha arribat el caçazombis Yamamura, s'han acabat les...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:37.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,El cadàver és al pis de dalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:37.24,White,,0,0,0,,Es pot saber què fa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Tu també has descobert l'assassí?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:43.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Jo només he ajudat en Heiji,\Nres més.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.40,White,,0,0,0,,Però que no era el senyor Harawaki,\Nl'assassí?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:50.48,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, en aquell vídeo que s'ha gravat\Nhem vist tots com atacava la Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,La prova és aquí,\Nés molt fàcil de veure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'Una mansió envoltada de zombis\N(Tercera part)'."
